  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为火灾监测系统设计一个星型模型，核心事实表记录每次火灾事件，周围环绕时间、地点和具体时刻三个维度表。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "fct_queimada",
        "dim_data_queimada",
        "dim_local_queimada",
        "dim_horarios_queimada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，您说的\"具体时刻\"维度是指精确到小时和分钟，而不是日期对吧？那我们需要把日期和时间拆成两个维度表。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dim_data_queimada",
        "dim_horarios_queimada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，dim_data_queimada管年月日这些日历属性，dim_horarios_queimada只管小时和分钟。这样分析时段分布的时候更灵活。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dim_data_queimada",
        "dim_horarios_queimada"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我开始构建结构。事实表fct_queimada用三个外键联合做主键：data_fk、local_fk、hora_fk，分别指向三个维度。同时存储火灾强度指标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "fct_queimada",
        "data_fk",
        "local_fk",
        "hora_fk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "火灾强度指标需要包含risco_fogo火灾风险等级、FRP火辐射功率，还有dias_sem_chuva连续无雨天数这三个核心字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "fct_queimada",
        "risco_fogo",
        "FRP",
        "dias_sem_chuva"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，事实表结构已添加。现在处理dim_local_queimada地点维度，需要涵盖从区域到具体坐标的地理信息层级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dim_local_queimada",
        "regiao_uf",
        "nome_municipio",
        "latitude",
        "longitude"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "地点维度要细化到市级，包含regiao_uf大区、sigla_uf州缩写、nome_uf州全称、nome_municipio市名，还有经纬度和bioma生物群落类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dim_local_queimada",
        "regiao_uf",
        "sigla_uf",
        "nome_uf",
        "nome_municipio",
        "bioma"
