    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，地点维度主键用local_id，同时保留id_municipio作为业务标识符，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dim_local_queimada",
        "local_id",
        "id_municipio"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。现在看日期维度dim_data_queimada，需要支持多种时间聚合：年、月、日、季度、学期、周几、是否周末、季节等。",
      "elements_involved": [
