      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "所有表结构都定义好了。我来画关系线：dim_horarios_queimada通过hora_fk连接事实表，dim_data_queimada通过data_fk，dim_local_queimada通过local_fk。",
